  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5dd0827a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkXCwr0dZOBY5LAxJqkBibPnyOpjMswATa4OSMFDtVwDialRv29vdxjgfuFMhqaxBib1RrtOCarsicxug%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"border:1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);border-radius:12px;padding:0px 0px;margin:0 0px;color:inherit;font-weight:400;font-family:PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 0px 16px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">放假回来了，回来了，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">幸好假期内没发新模型了，现在火的是节前最后两天前后脚发布的DeepSeek-V3.2-Exp和GLM-4.6。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017516\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9037037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a8d14078&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXmnBqEMNkDE0jMzUiblxKyiaXWCic3icF8WlQP8zqIonHk3iaRiab3nb67VqnpaiaLp40jOqLDcDic8kjHzoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">一个降价75%，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">一个登顶Hugginface第一</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">和openrouter趋势榜第一</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017518\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71857a05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmnBqEMNkDE0jMzUiblxKyiaX0WusrhEyOEpjBfLjY6opbdkIgRsxLAx3MeHNricJZJu2GZJ5OH6HoKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017519\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7596439169139466\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1685\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=659f7686&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXmnBqEMNkDE0jMzUiblxKyiaXtQUzbzVKDeohicribsXicdkwjQmSzpktwXiaTUkvJQPDlneXeqWRLE7Syw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:1.8;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: inherit;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">那我立刻马上光速</span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2em;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;color: inherit;margin: 0;min-height: 20px;letter-spacing: auto;color: inherit;color: inherit;font-size: inheritpx;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;font-size: inherit;font-weight: 400;font-family: inherit;line-height: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: #1B1B1B;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;margin: 16px 0;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">立刻掏出假期整理好大模型噩梦级测试案例1.0版，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">平时自己测，看别人测，看大模型自己测，都快看腻了，花了点时间归纳了一下，截止到2025年10月9号，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">主流的单case测试（特指非数据集）主要分为物理模拟、SVG、前端设计、可交互3D四大类，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天我一口气全测完，还要带上DeepSeek V3.2，测评方式还是老规矩啊，公开所有提示语，每个模型跑三次，取效果最好的一次作为最终结果。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid rgb(173,130,247);border-radius:8px;padding:4px 14px;place-items:flex-start;display:flex;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left!important;\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;width:100%;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">有些提示语比较长，以及连同输出的代码和效果我都打包到文档了，公众号后台发“</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">ds</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">glm</span></span></span><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">”就好啦。</span></span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">先来个常见的物理模拟热热身，</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid rgb(173,130,247);border-radius:8px;padding:4px 14px;place-items:flex-start;display:flex;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left!important;\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;width:100%;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">用 HTML、CSS 和 JavaScript 实现这样一个效果：一个小球被困在一个旋转的六边形内部。小球受到地球重力的作用，并与六边形内壁产生摩擦。小球的弹跳需要看起来逼真自然。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.6：</span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-weight: bold;color: #000000 !important;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek V3.2：</span></span></p>\n    <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然没明说，但GLM-4.6和DeepSeek V3.2不约而同都选择了提供参数调整项，可以重置小球，加速和减速六边形的旋转速度，还可以取消动力，我记得DeepSeek R1那会小球能模拟出重力就已经算厉害的了。GLM-4.6还增加了重力参数，小球大小，甚至还有摩擦力。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">再来试试看画SVG，</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid rgb(173,130,247);border-radius:8px;padding:4px 14px;place-items:flex-start;display:flex;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left!important;\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;width:100%;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">绘制一个骑自行车的鹈鹕的 SVG 图像</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017511\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3277777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=449fb393&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXkXCwr0dZOBY5LAxJqkBibPnP1UFQiahMkyDuO3jrJmqvHqFmrmn9M2fsX7r1OHrtuQjn9SnjNBSZrg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这也是一个成名已久的超绝测试了，</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">GLM-4.6（左侧）基本上元素都画出来了，有板有眼的，就是鹈鹕坐的位置有点低，DeepSeek V3.2（右侧）画出来的鹈鹕实现了脚身分离，方向也反了，车把也没了。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我还找到了另外16个模型的跑出来的鹈鹕，有的车把没了，有的鸟没了，有的头反方向了，有的都不在车丧，甚至有的车都没有画出来。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n     <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017473\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8feb647f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXkXCwr0dZOBY5LAxJqkBibPnlJFvejbJicIZ3dORBdMQXE7fCwJicuJ2TPcGcUABaP4DX5ha2rguIJ3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">就这个测试它居然还有升级版，让鹈鹕骑自己。。。。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid rgb(173,130,247);border-radius:8px;padding:4px 14px;place-items:flex-start;display:flex;margin-bottom:20px;text-align:left!important;\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:16px 0;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:auto;width:100%;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;\"><span style=\"color: inherit;author: 7231935989239840796;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">绘制一幅鹈鹕骑着另一只鹈鹕的 SVG 图像</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100017512\" class=\"rich_pag